'\"! tbl|mmdoc
'\"macro stdmacro
.TH INFORM 1G
.SH NAME
inform \- display a message in a window
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B inform
[text]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I inform
opens up a window on the graphics console containing the \f2text\f1
and a Continue button.  If the mouse is clicked in the Continue button, the
window will go away.
.SH BUGS
The window which appears is fixed size, and the text is not wrapped, so a lengthy
message can be truncated.
.SH SEE ALSO
confirm(1G)
